	"title"		"RMR REBORN fan work [Workshop]"
	"description"		"[h2]About This Version[/h2]\nThis mod is an unofficial derivative maintenance version based on [i]RogueLike Mod REBORN[/i]. I greatly enjoyed the original mod and wanted to experience more content beyond where its development ended, so I began maintaining and expanding it after official updates ceased.\n\nEvery journey begins at Urban Myth. Players must choose between Normal Battles, Elite Battles, Boss Battles, Shops, Rest Sites, and Mysterious Events while gradually building their team and advancing toward the Impuritas Civitatis endgame.\n\nThis page contains spoilers for the later chapters and ending content of [i]Library of Ruina[/i].\n\nThis version does not represent the original creator, the REBORN team, or Project Moon.\n[h2]Major Changes[/h2]\n[list]\n[*][b]Redesigned RMR Entry and Start Menu[/b]\n\nThe RMR icon in the upper-right corner of the Reception screen now opens a full-screen start menu.\n\nFrom this menu, you can start a new run, continue your current journey, challenge Floor Realizations, view the gameplay guide, access the Permanent Compendium, reset permanent progression, or exit.\n\n[*][b]Added Floor Realization Challenges[/b]\n\nYou can now independently challenge the final Realization battle of each of the ten original Floors.\n\nClearing a Floor Realization for the first time permanently unlocks that Floor's exclusive Abnormality Pages and E.G.O., allowing them to appear in future reward pools and Shop selections.\n\nPreviously cleared Realizations can be challenged again, but their first-clear rewards cannot be obtained more than once.\n\n[*][b]Reworked Abnormality Page Acquisition[/b]\n\nMost regular Abnormality Pages are now obtained through random post-battle rewards, Shops, special events, and other sources.\n\nAbnormality Pages and E.G.O. exclusive to a Floor Realization will only be added to future selection pools after that Floor has been cleared for the first time.\n\n[*][b]Added a Permanent Compendium[/b]\n\nThe Permanent Compendium records all unlocked Key Pages, Combat Pages, Abnormality Pages, and E.G.O.\n\nYou can also use it to inspect their attributes, abilities, and upgraded effects.\n\nWhen challenging a Floor Realization, you can use content recorded in the Permanent Compendium to assemble a temporary team.\n\nAfter the challenge ends, your original run configuration will be restored. The temporary setup will not overwrite or interfere with your normal run save.\n\nThe Permanent Compendium is not the starting inventory for a new run. After beginning a new journey, you must still collect resources and build your team again from scratch.\n\n[*][b]Expanded the Impuritas Civitatis Chapter[/b]\n\nThe standard route now extends into Impuritas Civitatis and includes several Impuritas Civitatis-level Receptions.\n\nPossible final bosses include The Black Silence and the Distorted Reverberation Ensemble. Each run will feature one of them as its final encounter.\n\nDefeating each boss for the first time will also permanently unlock special content, providing additional rewards for future runs.\n\n[*][b]Added Abnormality Battle Nodes[/b]\n\nStarting from Chapter 3, Abnormality Battles may appear along the route.\n\nThese encounters function as high-risk, high-reward Elite Battles and provide additional opportunities to obtain Abnormality Pages.\n\nAbnormality Battle nodes will not appear during Chapters 1 or 2. Any such positions will instead be replaced with Rest Sites.\n[/list]\n[h2]Before Subscribing[/h2]\n[list]\n[*]This version uses the same internal mod ID as the original RMR. Do not enable both versions at the same time. It is recommended that you keep only one of them installed or enabled.\n\n[*]The Continue option is located in the RMR start menu. It will only appear when a valid run save exists.\n\n[*]Starting a new run will overwrite your current run save. Permanent Compendium progress, Floor Realization clear records, and first-clear records for special bosses are stored separately and will be preserved.\n\n[*]Before switching between versions or installing a major update, it is recommended that you back up the [b]LogueSave[/b] save directory.\n\n[*]Known major mod conflict: [url=https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=2868713582]Sayo to Everyone[/url].\n\n[*]Simplified Chinese is currently the primary language used for development, maintenance, and testing. English and Korean text are included, but their completeness and accuracy still require further review.\n\n[*]After updating the mod, fully close and restart the game before playing.\n[/list]\n[h2]Bug Reports[/h2]\nThis version is currently developed and maintained by one person with AI assistance. Testing coverage is limited, so issues involving progression, UI display, localization, or mod compatibility may still occur.\n\nIf you encounter a problem, please report it in the comments section of this page.\n\nWhen reporting an issue, please include as much of the following information as possible:\n\n[list]\n[*]Your game language\n\n[*]Your enabled mod list\n\n[*]The current chapter and node\n\n[*]Steps required to reproduce the issue\n\n[*]Relevant screenshots\n\n[*]The Build information and exception messages from [b]Player.log[/b]\n[/list]\nProviding this information will make it much easier to identify and resolve the problem.\n\n[h2]Additional Information[/h2]\n[list]\n[*]If you enjoy the mod, please consider joining the original creator's Discord server and showing your support:\n\n[url=https://discord.com/invite/buC2SHRRGk]RogueLike Mod REBORN Discord[/url]\n\n[*]If you would like to create another derivative version based on this project, the source code is available here:\n\n[url=https://github.com/NakashimaYuki0912/NakashimaYuki0912.github.io]GitHub Repository[/url]\n\nPlease contact me on Discord before beginning your derivative project.\n[/list]"
	"changenote"		"[h2]2026-07-21 Update[/h2]\n[list]\n[*][b]Floor Realization reward isolation[/b]: Realization-exclusive Abnormality Pages and E.G.O. are now strictly gated behind each Floor's first Realization clear (triple-checked by passive ID range, script whitelist and unique-level).\n[*]Normal battle reward pools, shop pools and permanent-tier unlock pools no longer leak locked Realization-exclusive pages.\n[*]Loading an existing run save now sanitizes any locked exclusive pages that leaked in from older versions.\n[/list]\n\n[h2]2026-07-21 更新[/h2]\n[list]\n[*][b]解放战奖励隔离[/b]：解放战专属异想体书页与E.G.O现在严格绑定各楼层解放战首通解锁（被动ID段、脚本白名单、Unique等级三重校验）。\n[*]普通战斗奖励池、商店池与永久层级解锁池不再混入未解锁的解放战专属书页。\n[*]读取旧存档时会自动清理此前版本混入的未解锁专属书页。\n[/list]"
}